Question.question_text:
I don't know why I am getting this 3d effect in words. How can I remove the effect and flatten the words?
The font family is Poppins
   body {font-family: "Poppins";}

answer_code:
text-shadow: none;


.text-class
{
    text-shadow: none;
    background: #333;
    color: #fff;
}

